{
  "stem": "27340.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was a training farm, one of six or seven in the country, and this was situated in Bosham in Hampshire between Chichester and Portsmouth, or as the locals call it, Pompey and Chi.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there we had a building.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It had been a-- a I don't quite know how to call this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It used to be a recuperation home, a rest home, a rest home for employees of Gestetner.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Gestetner was a large company.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Sigmund Gestetner himself was a very ardent Zionist.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He had established another rest home for his employees, and he'd made this over to the Zionist organization.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there were about 40 of us there, boys and girls, and we were fundamentally all city dwellers, city people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so it was a question of getting used to two major items.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "First of all, hard, physical work, and that was not too difficult.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the other aspect, obviously, was to live in a community, to have basically nothing or everything.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "In other words, you had no private property, and everything belonged to the commune.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So on Friday nights, for instance, to give you an example, we would always have a Shabbat meal, and we would always have a sing song, and we would always put up a show of some sort of entertainment, sometimes of a very high cultural standard.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Many of these people were highly cultured individuals from universities, academically well-qualified, technically well-qualified, militarily well-qualified.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was after the Second World War.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had a number of people of the rank of officers, and so on, in the British forces there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Age ranged between 18 and perhaps 26 or 27, and boys and girls were living there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And on Fridays, when we came back from work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of course, we'd have showers, and we'd shave.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
